org.graalvm.word

Interface UnsignedWord

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ComparableWord, WordBase
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Pointer

    public interface UnsignedWord
extends ComparableWord
    Represents an unsigned word-sized value.

    19.0
